\id BAK - Amele NT and Genesis [aey] -Papua New Guinea 1997 (DBL 2014)
\h DADO MEC
\toc2 DADO MEC
\toc1 DADO MEC
\mt1 Iwaladec Je Leih Megecnu Dado Mec
\s1 Anut uqa odi bilina
\m 1. Memige Anut uqa odi bilina.
\pi1 Mak 10.27; 12.29-30; Luk 1.37; 6.35-36; Jon 4.23-24; Aposel 14.14-17; 17.22-31; Rom 1.18-23; 11.33-36; 1 Korin 8.4-6; 2 Korin 1.3; 1 Timoti 1.17; 6.15-16; Hibru 4.13; 10.30-31; Jems 1.17; 1 Pita 1.14-17; 1 Jon 1.5; 4.7-12; 4.16; Jud 24-25; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 4.8-11; 15.3-4.
\m 2. Anut Melah, Jisas Krais, uqa odi bilina.
\pi1 Jisas Krais uqa Anut Melah.
\pi1 Matju 11.27-30; 16.13-17; Luk 1.35; Jon 1.1-18; 5.19-29; 6.35-40; 8.58; 11.25-27; 14.5-11; 17.1-5; 20.26-31; Aposel 3.13-16; 4.10-12; Rom 1.3-4; 1 Korin 3.11; 2 Korin 4.4-6; 5.21; Galesia 4.4-5; Filipai 2.5-11; Kolosi 1.15-20; 2.9-10; Hibru 1.1-14; 7.26-28; 1 Jon 2.1-2; 5.20; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 1.12-18; 19.11-16.
\pi1 Anut Melah uqa dana caleceb caja basecdon.
\pi1 Jon 1.14; Luk 1.26-38; Matju 1.18-25; Luk 2.1-20; Matju 2.1-23; Galesia 4.4-5; Filipai 2.6-7; Hibru 2.14-18.
\pi1 Jisas uqa dana cajaca me je iwalaadei hagca me maden.
\pi1 Matju 4.23-25; 7.28-29; 9.35-36; 11.1-6; Luk 4.14-44; Aposel 10.36-38, Jon 20.30-31.
\pi1 Jisas kobolkobol odoc mati odon.
\pi1 Matju 8.1-4; 8.5-13; 8.14-15; 8.23-27; 8.28-33; 9.1-7; 9.18-26; 9.27-31; 9.32-33; 12.9-14; 12.22; 14.15-21; 14.22-32; 15.22-28; 15.32-38; 17.14-18; 20.29-34; 21.18-22; Mak 1.21-28; 7.32-37; 8.22-25; Luk 5.4-8; 7.11-15; 13.10-13; 14.1-4; 17.12-14; 22.50-51; Jon 2.1-11; 4.46-54; 5.5-9; 9.1-7; 11.11-44; 21.4-6; Aposel 2.22.
\pi1 Juda agena iloilo age Jisas hewudimeig uqa qocobil cal migian ec madein.
\pi1 Matju 26.47-68; 27.1-2; 27.11-31; Mak 14.43-65; 15.1-20; Luk 22.47-53; 22.63-71; 23.1-25; Jon 18.1-14; 18.19-24; 18.28-19.16.
\pi1 Age Jisas na babalecna tuitu qumeig caqusecebil caculimei cal men.
\pi1 Matju 27.32-56; Mak 15.21-41; Luk 23.26-49; Jon 19.17-37.
\pi1 Age Jisas heel cisein.
\pi1 Matju 27.57-66; Mak 15.42-47; Luk 23.50-56; Jon 19.38-42.
\pi1 Jisas cal mecnadec ceseli cajeceb leih age fecidoin.
\pi1 Matju 28.1-20; Mak 16.1-8; Luk 24.1-49; Jon 20.1-21.14; Aposel 1.3-8; 2.24-32; 3.15; 4.10; 4.33; 10.39-43; 13.29-39; 17.2-3; 17.30-31; Rom 1.4; 4.24-25; 1 Korin 15.3-8; 15.12-21; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 1.18.
\pi1 Jisas sao jobon ohis ceseli ten.
\pi1 Luk 24.50-51; Aposel 1.9-11; 2.32-36; 5.30-31; Rom 8.34; Efesas 1.20-23; Filipai 2.9-11; Hibru 1.3-11; 2.9; 4.14-16; 7.25-26; 10.12-14; 1 Pita 3.22.
\m 3. Kis Gun uqa odi bilina.
\pi1 Matju 28.19; Mak 1.9-11; 3.28-30; Luk 1.35; 3.16; 4.1; 11.13; 12.12 Jon 1.32-34; 3.5-8; 7.37-39; 14.15-17; 14.26; 15.26; 16.7-15; 20.19-23; Aposel 1.4-5; 1.8; 2.1-18; 2.38-39; 4.31; 5.3-5; 8.14-17; 10.44-48; 13.2-4; 15.28; 16.7-10; 19.1-7; Rom 5.5; 7.6; 8.9-16; 8.26-27; 1 Korin 2.4; 2.9-16; 3.16; 6.11; 6.19; 12.1-13; 2 Korin 1.21-22; 5.5; 13.14; Galesia 3.2-5; 4.6; 5.16-18; 5.22-25; Efesas 1.13-14; 1.17; 3.16; 4.3-4; 4.30; 5.18-20; 6.17-18; 1 Tesalonaika 1.5-6; 5.19; 2 Tesalonaika 2.13; Taitas 3.5-6; Hibru 2.4; 9.14; 1 Pita 1.2; 1.11; 2 Pita 1.20-21; 1 Jon 2.20; 3.24; 4.13; 5.6-8.
\m 4. Anut uqa ceteteh cunug ifanaden.
\pi1 Matju 19.4; Jon 1.3; Aposel 14.15; 17.24-26; 1 Korin 8.6; Kolosi 1.15-16; Hibru 1.2; 11.3; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 4.11.
\m 5. Anut uqa ceteteh cunug cofadena.
\pi1 Matju 6.25-34; 10.29-31; Aposel 14.15-17; Rom 8.28; 11.36; Kolosi 1.17; Hibru 1.3; Jems 4.13-16.
\s1 Dana cajaca age odi bilegina
\m 6. Dana cajaca cunug age silail mein.
\pi1 Jon 8.7-9; Rom 3.9-20; 3.23; 5.12; Galesia 3.22; 1 Jon 1.8-10.
\m 7. Dana cajaca age silail megina saen euna age odi bilegina.
\pi1 Rom 1.18-32; 8.5-8; Galesia 5.19-21; Efesas 2.1-3; 5.3-5; Kolosi 3.5-10; Jems 4.17; 1 Pita 4.3; 1 Jon 3.4-5.
\m 8. Anut uqa dana cajaca qee cahahaadecebfi age agena silailnu Anutna geladec bisalu bilegina.
\pi1 Matju 10.28; 13.41-42; Jon 3.18-20; 3.36; Aposel 17.30-31; Rom 1.18-19; 6.23; Galesia 6.7-8; Kolosi 3.5-6; 2 Tesalonaika 1.7-9; Hibru 9.27; 10.26-31; 1 Pita 1.17; 4.3-5; Jud 7; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 20.11-15.
\s1 Anut uqa dana cajaca agena silailnadec odi cahahaadena
\m 9. Anut dana cajaca cunugnu nalunuga mena, odimei uqa cahahaadecnu gale dona.
\pi1 Jon 3.16; Rom 5.8; 1 Timoti 2.3-6; 2 Pita 3.9; 1 Jon 4.9-10.
\m 10. Anut Melah, Jisas Krais, cahahagecnu cal men.
\pi1 Mak 10.45; Jon 3.16; Rom 4.25; 5.8; 1 Korin 15.3-4; 2 Korin 5.19-21; Galesia 3.13; 1 Timoti 2.5-6; Hibru 2.9; 9.28; 1 Pita 1.18-20; 2.24-25; 3.18; 1 Jon 2.2; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 5.8-10.
\m 11. Jisas golac egena silailnu ameg cagasigen.
\pi1 Matju 26.26-29; Rom 3.25; 5.9-10; Efesas 1.7; Hibru 9.11-14; 1 Jon 1.6-7; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 7.14-17.
\m 12. Anut uqa egena silail cagasigena.
\pi1 Aposel 5.31; 10.43; 26.18; Efesas 1.7; 4.32; Kolosi 1.13-14; 2.13-14; Hibru 10.17-18; 1 Jon 1.8-10.
\m 13. Anut odigeceb ege uqa amegna dana cajaca ititom tawoqona.
\pi1 Aposel 13.38-39; Rom 1.16-17; 3.21-26; 5.1; 5.18-19; Galesia 2.16; 3.6-9; Taitas 3.7.
\m 14. Anut uqa cebac bilec haun igina.
\pi1 Jon 3.1-16; 5.19-29; 10.10; 11.25-26; 14.6; 17.2-3; 20.31; Rom 5.21; 6.5-14; 8.10-17; 2 Korin 5.17; Galesia 2.20; Efesas 2.1-6; Kolosi 2.13; 3.1-4; 2 Timoti 1.10; Taitas 3.4-7; 1 Pita 1.23; 1 Jon 5.11-13.
\m 15. Anut odigeceb ege uqa talacul biluquna.
\pi1 Jon 1.12-13; Rom 8.14-17; Galesia 4.6-7; Hibru 12.5-11; 1 Jon 3.1-3.
\s1 Anut cahahagecnu gale dona eu dumeb ege odi odeqan
\m 16. Egena silailnu walol geceb silailnu tului falicdumeb haun qee odeqaun.
\pi1 Matju 4.17; Mak 6.12; Luk 13.1-5; 15.1-31; 24.45-47; Aposel 2.37-40; 3.19-20; 17.29-31; 20.21; 26.19-20; 2 Korin 7.8-11; 2 Pita 3.9; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 9.20-21.
\m 17. Ege Jisas cahahagecnu wawige meleigian.
\pi1 Jon 1.12; 3.15-18; 3.36; 6.47; 14.6; 20.31; Aposel 4.12; 16.30-31; Rom 3.20-22; 10.9-10; Galesia 2.16; Efesas 2.8-9.
\m 18. Ege Anutca, ege eeta odeqan gale donaca eu docnu uqana jaqec je sanijeqan.
\pi1 Matju 4.1-4; 5.17-20; 22.29; Jon 8.31-32; 20.31; Aposel 20.32; Rom 15.4; 16.26; Kolosi 3.16; 1 Tesalonaika 2.13; 1 Timoti 4.13; 2 Timoti 3.14-17; Hibru 4.12; 1 Pita 1.22-25; 2 Pita 1.19-21; 2 Jon 9-10; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 1.3.
\m 19. Ege wa joigec oqan.
\pi1 Matju 28.18-20; Jon 3.22; 4.1-2; Aposel 2.37-42; 8.12; 8.36-38; 10.44-48; 16.14-15; 16.31-33; 19.1-7; 22.12-16; Rom 6.1-4; Galesia 3.26-27; Kolosi 2.12; 1 Pita 3.20-22.
\m 20. Ege wawige meleec cotigeil gami gaid ceguleqan.
\pi1 Matju 18.19-20; Aposel 2.41-47; Rom 12.4-8; Efesas 1.22-23; 4.11-16; Kolosi 3.15-17; 1 Timoti 4.13; Hibru 10.24-25.
\m 21. Ege wawige meleec cotigeil gami cegulimeb Tibudna bred wain gabinca gaid jeqan.
\pi1 Matju 26.26-30; Mak 14.22-26; Luk 22.14-20; 1 Korin 10.14-22; 11.17-34.
\s1 Ege Jisas Kraisnu wawige meleena ege odi cobeqan
\m 22. Ege Anut, ege Memigeca, Jisas Krais, egena Tibudca, conola toodu odeqan.
\pi1 Jon 14.15; 14.21; 14.23-24; 15.10-17; Rom 13.8-10; 1 Pita 1.14-16; 1 Jon 2.3-8; 3.22-24; 2 Jon 5-6.
\m 23. Ege Anutnu nalug meqan, odocob dana cajacanu nalunuga meqan.
\pi1 Matju 22.34-40; Mak 12.28-34; Luk 10.25-37; Jon 14.21; 1 Jon 5.3; Matju 5.43-48; Jon 13.34-35; 15.12-17; Rom 12.9-10; 13.8-10; 1 Korin 13.1-3; 16.14; Galesia 5.13-15; 1 Tesalonaika 4.9-10; 1 Pita 1.8; 4.8; 1 Jon 2.9-11; 3.11-18; 4.7-21.
\m 24. Ege Krais duman cicilon oqan.
\pi1 Jon 13.34-35; 14.27; Rom 12.9-13; Galesia 5.22-26; Kolosi 3.12-17; 1 Tesalonaika 5.16-18.
\m 25. Ege inondoqan. \it Ege odi inondoqan.\it*
\pi1 Matju 6.5-13; 7.7-11; 18.19-20; Mak 11.24-25; Luk 11.1-13; 18.1-8; 21.36; Jon 14.13-14; 15.7; 16.23-26; Rom 8.26-27; 12.12; Efesas 2.18; 6.18; Filipai 4.6-7; Kolosi 4.2; 1 Tesalonaika 5.17; 1 Timoti 2.1-4; 2.8; 4.4-5; Hibru 4.16; 10.19-22; Jems 1.5-8; 4.2-3; 5.13-18; 1 Pita 4.7; 1 Jon 3.21-22; 5.14-15. \it Leih age odi inondoin.\it*
\pi1 Matju 11.25-26; 14.23; 19.13-15; Mak 1.35; Luk 5.16; 6.12; 22.32; 22.39-46; Jon 11.41-42; 17.1-26; Aposel 4.24-31; 16.25; 20.36; 21.5; Rom 1.9-10; 10.1-2; 15.30-33; 2 Korin 12.7-10; Efesas 1.15-20; 3.14-21; 6.19-20; Filipai 1.3-5; 1.9-11; Kolosi 1.9-12; 4.3-4; 1 Tesalonaika 3.9-13; 2 Tesalonaika 1.11-12; 3.1-5; Hibru 5.7; 7.25.
\m 26. Ege gaidgaid Anut hegaga doqan.
\pi1 Luk 17.11-19; Jon 6.11; Rom 1.21; Efesas 5.20; Filipai 4.4-7; Kolosi 2.7; 3.17; 4.2; 1 Tesalonaika 5.18; 1 Timoti 2.1; 4.4-5.
\m 27. Ege dana cajaca cesuladeqan.
\pi1 Matju 6.1-4; 7.12; 25.31-46; Luk 3.10-11; 6.38; Aposel 11.27-30; 1 Korin 10.24; 2 Korin 8.1-15; 9.1-15; Galesia 6.9-10; Filipai 4.14-19; Hibru 10.24; 13.1-3; 13.16; Jems 1.27; 2.15-16; 1 Jon 3.16-18.
\m 28. Egedodoc jogoi wawige lal qocca bileqan.
\pi1 Matju 5.3-12; 18.1-5; Luk 14.7-11; 18.9-14; Efesas 4.2; Filipai 2.3-11; Kolosi 3.12-13; Jems 4.5-10; 1 Pita 5.5-7.
\m 29. Ege cehewanigeca, egena cetetehca odi cisdoqan.
\pi1 Matju 6.19-21; 6.24-34; Luk 12.13-21; 12.32-34; Aposel 20.35; 1 Timoti 6.6-10; 6.17-19; Hibru 13.5-6; Jems 2.1-9; 5.1-6.
\m 30. Eu ihoc nijecebfi ege dana dewenigenu je um qigen eu gesilec jona ehudi lecnu bitecdoqan.
\pi1 Matju 5.25-26; 5.38-42; 18.15-17; Rom 12.14-21; 1 Korin 6.1-8.
\m 31. Dana egena ilo bilegina eu conoga toodu odeqan.
\pi1 Matju 22.15-22; Aposel 5.27-29; Rom 13.1-7; 1 Timoti 2.1-4; Taitas 3.1; 1 Pita 2.13-17.
\m 32. Ege kadan tibudnu cain cuha feqaun.
\pi1 Matju 4.10; Aposel 17.22-31; 1 Korin 5.11; 6.9-11; 8.1-13; 10.1-22; 2 Korin 6.14-18; Galesia 5.19-21;1 Tesalonaika 1.9-10; 1 Jon 5.21; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 21.8; 22.15.
\m 33. Ege dool cain ihaneqaun.
\pi1 Matju 9.13; Mak 12.33; Rom 12.1; Hibru 9.6-10.18.
\m 34. Ege dana osona caja cain oqaun, odocob ege wal kobol cain odeqaun.
\pi1 Matju 5.27-30; Jon 8.2-11; Rom 13.8-10; 1 Korin 5.9-11; 6.9-20; Galesia 5.19; Efesas 5.3; Kolosi 3.5-6; 1 Tesalonaika 4.1-8; Hibru 13.4; Jud 7.
\m 35. Ege ceu jecomun dalul cain qigiaun.
\pi1 Rom 13.13; 1 Korin 5.11; 6.9-11; Galesia 5.19-21; Efesas 5.18; 1 Timoti 3.1-3; Taitas 1.7; 1 Pita 4.3-5.
\s1 Krais tamanec age odi bilegina
\m 36. Tamanec agena dana cajaca age odi biluqagan.
\pi1 Matju 16.13-20; Aposel 2.41-42; Rom 12.4-8; 1 Korin 12.12-30; Efesas 1.22-23; 2.19-22; 4.1-16; Kolosi 1.18; Hibru 10.24-25; 1 Pita 2.4-10; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 19.5-10.
\m 37. Tamanec cofgec ege nesili ehadoqona age dumanaga eu odi biligian.
\pi1 Aposel 6.1-6; Aposel 14.23; 1 Timoti 3.1-13; Taitas 1.5-9.
\m 38. Tamanec cofadec age odi coboqagan.
\pi1 Matju 28.18-20; Luk 22.24-27; Aposel 20.17-35; 1 Tesalonaika 2.1-12; 1 Timoti 4.1-16, 2 Timoti 2.1-26, 3.10-17, 4.1-5; Taitas 2.7-8; 1 Pita 5.1-4.
\m 39. Ege tamanec cofgec conoga toodu odeqan.
\pi1 1 Korin 9.14; Galesia 6.6; 1 Tesalonaika 5.12-13; 1 Timoti 5.17-22; Hibru 13.7; 13.17.
\s1 Dana talac eu odi bilegina
\m 40. Gemugail aidegailca age odi biluqagan.
\pi1 Matju 19.4-6; 1 Korin 7.1-16; Efesas 5.21-33; Kolosi 3.18-19; Taitas 2.3-5; Hibru 13.4; 1 Pita 3.1-7.
\m 41. Melemegail atenegailca age odi biluqagan.
\pi1 Matju 15.3-6; Luk 2.51; Efesas 6.1-3; Kolosi 3.20; 1 Timoti 5.4; 5.8; Hibru 12.7-11.
\m 42. Memegail anagailca age odi biluqagan.
\pi1 Efesas 6.4; Kolosi 3.21; 1 Timoti 3.4-5.
\m 43. Caja wij age odi biluqagan.
\pi1 Aposel 6.1; Rom 7.2-3; 1 Korin 7.39-40; 1 Timoti 5.3-16; Jems 1.27.
\m 44. Ege dana caja sisi jelec cain cagoqaun.
\pi1 Matju 5.31-32, 19.3-9; Luk 16.18; Rom 7.2-3; 1 Korin 7.10-16.
\s1 Kristen age culumen gaid gulucdogina
\m 45. Age sogoec gahidocnu saciadoc biluqagan.
\pi1 Rom 8.18-25; 8.28; 2 Korin 1.4; 4.16-18; Jems 1.2-4; 1 Pita 1.6-9; 2.19-21; 5.8-10.
\m 46. Age aaqati tootooadec gahidocnu saciadoc biluqagan.
\pi1 Matju 5.10-12; Mak 13.9-13; Luk 12.4-9; Jon 15.18-21; 16.1-4; Aposel 5.41; Rom 8.35-37; 12.12-14; 12.17-21; 1 Korin 4.11-13; 2 Korin 4.8-11; 12.10; Filipai 1.28-29; 2 Tesalonaika 1.4-8; 3.2-4; 2 Timoti 3.10-13; Hibru 10.32-39; 12.3-4; 1 Pita 3.13-17; 4.12-19; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 2.10.
\m 47. Age cal moqagannu cucuiecnu qee nijel.
\pi1 Jon 6.39-40, 11.17-27, 14.1-4; Rom 8.10-11; 8.38-39; 14.7-9; 1 Korin 15.12-58; 2 Korin 5.1-10; Filipai 1.20-24; 1 Tesalonaika 4.13-18; Hibru 2.14-15; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 14.13; 21.1-4, 22.1-5.
\m 48. Anut uqa cemenega bibilei cesuladena.
\pi1 Matju 18.19-20; 28.19-20; Jon 14.16-23; Rom 8.35-39; 2 Korin 6.16-18; Efesas 3.17-19; Filipai 4.13; Kolosi 2.6-7; 2 Tesalonaika 3.16; Hibru 13.5-6.
\m 49. Seten uqa Kristen waadecnu odona.
\pi1 Matju 13.19; Luk 4.1-13; 22.3-4; Jon 8.42-44; 2 Korin 2.10-11; 4.4; 11.13-15; Efesas 2.2; 1 Tesalonaika 2.18; 2 Tesalonaika 2.9-12; 1 Pita 5.8-9; 1 Jon 3.8-10; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 12.7-12; 20.1-3; 20.10.
\m 50. Anut uqa Seten teidocnuca, culumen gahidocnuca gagadic ihoc adena.
\pi1 Matju 4.1-11; 6.13; Luk 22.31-32; Jon 17.14-19; Rom 8.31-39; 12.12; 16.19-20; 1 Korin 10.12-13; 16.13; 2 Korin 12.7-10; Efesas 3.20-21; 6.10-18; Filipai 4.13; 1 Tesalonaika 3.5-8; 2 Tesalonaika 3.3; 2 Timoti 1.7-8; Hibru 2.18; 4.14-16; 12.1-2; Jems 4.7; 1 Pita 1.5; 5.8-11; 1 Jon 4.4; 5.3-5; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 12.7-12.
\m 51. Anut uqa dana caja hagca me madena.
\pi1 Matju 4.23-25; 9.35; 11.2-5; Aposel 3.1-6; 8.4-8; 19.11-16; 28.8-9; 1 Korin 12.9; 12.29-30; 2 Korin 12.7-10; 1 Timoti 5.23; 2 Timoti 4.20; Jems 5.14-15.
\s1 Cel ceteh hibna caloqagan
\m 52. Jisas uqa mahana ceseli nigian.
\pi1 Matju 24.29-44; Jon 14.1-3; Aposel 1.10-11; 3.19-21; Filipai 3.20-21; Kolosi 3.4; 1 Tesalonaika 1.9-10; 3.13; 4.13-5.11; 2 Tesalonaika 1.6-10; 2.1-4; 1 Timoti 6.13-15; 2 Timoti 4.8; Hibru 9.28; 2 Pita 3.1-18; 1 Jon 3.1-3; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 1.7; 22.12-13.
\m 53. Anut uqa Jisas Krais umna dana cajaca cunug gesiladigian.
\pi1 Matju 7.21-23; 16.24-27; 25.31-46; Jon 3.18-21; 5.24-29; Aposel 17.30-31; Rom 2.1-11; 14.10-12; 1 Korin 3.10-15; 4.5; 2 Korin 5.9-10; 2 Tesalonaika 1.5-10; Hibru 9.27-28; 10.26-31; 1 Pita 1.17; 4.3-5; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 20.11-15.
\m 54. Anut cahahaadigian eundec age sao jobon biluqagan.
\pi1 Luk 12.32-34; Jon 14.1-3; 2 Korin 5.1-8; Filipai 1.23; 1 Pita 1.4-5; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 4.1-11; 21.1-4; 21.22-22.5; 22.14-15.
\m 55. Anut qee cahahaadeiaun eundec age oloqanihna biluqagan.
\pi1 Matju 10.28; 13.41-42; 47-50; 25.41; Luk 16.23-26; 2 Tesalonaika 1.9; Jahunec Je Camasac Mudec 20.10-15; 21.8. 
